from.S: base.locations INNER JOIN base.games g ON locations.location_id = g.location_id AND date_part(year, g.date_created) = 2018 AND g.is_data_verified = TRUE AND g.application_type <> 3 AND g.game_reference NOT LIKE '%-BP-%' INNER JOIN dict.game_type d ON d.game_type = g.game_type

select.S: locations.location_id, locations.name, g.game_type, d.game_type_string AS level, count(g.game_id) AS count, row_number() over (PARTITION BY locations.location_id ORDER BY count desc) as num, getdate() as date_processed
